                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1619" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0049</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9150 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浩天公司的供应链融资之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Case Study on the Supply Chain Financing of Haotian Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曲英，刘越等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浩天通讯设备连锁企业经营管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链融资；经营模式；应收账款融资模式；融资产品；中小企业；2014百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Supply Chain Financing; Operation Model; Account Receivable Financing Patterns; Financing Product; SMEs</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">融资难一直是束缚中小企业发展的重要瓶颈。尽管我国政府和金融机构制定了一系列相关政策，仍未能有效解决这一问题。本案例描述了浩天公司如何针对自身经营模式及其与核心企业辽宁移动的合作模式进行供应链融资的。浩天公司的 “买手机送话费”和“存话费送手机” 经营模式要求其为辽宁移动垫付手机和话费款，导致企业资金严重不足，为此企业提出了供应链应收账款融资思路；通过调查及与辽宁移动沟通，浦发银行设计出符合浩天资金需求的供应链融资产品，从而实现了三方共赢。通过本案例学习，可以了解中小企业融资难背景，理解供应链应收账款融资的内涵和模式，掌握有效实施供应链应收账款融资的条件，为解决中小企业融资难困境提供了有益的参考和借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The difficulty in financing has been an important bottleneck for the development of small and medium enterprises (SMEs). Although many relevant policies have been issued by Chinese governments and financial institutes, the problem has still not been solved effectively. This case describes the initial practices of Haotian, an SEM, in its supply chain financing. Its operation models, “buy phone get call free” and “pay call get phone free”, require Haotian to pay in advance for Liaoning Mobile to purchase phones or to pay cell phones bills for costumers, which led Haotian into the serious lack of money. In order to raise money, Haotian put forward the accounts receivable financing patterns based on the supply chain perspective. After the investigation on the supply chain and discussion with Liaoning Mobile, the SPD Bank designed for Haotian financing products, which brought triple-win. This case is helpful to understand the background of difficulty in financing for SEMs, and the content and the patterns of supply chain accounts receivable financing and also helpful to grasp how to effectively implement supply chain accounts receivable financing, which is a beneficial reference for SEMs to solve the difficulty in financing. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《金融学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链融资应收账款模式及其风险识别与控制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-08</td>
                            </tr>
